Maintainer: Jamie Reilly <jamie_reilly@temple.edu>
Description: Generates a wide range of text analytics describing one or more language samples. Variables include common discourse descriptors such as sentence length, word frequency, type-token ratio, token count, word length, etc. The package computes descriptive statistics for each metric and outputs values as a publication ready table if specified by the user. 
